## Threat [/single_threat_data]

### /single_threat_data/?q=THREAT   [GET]

Retrieves data for a specific threat: name, timing, severity, associated animals/habitats.

Example: Let's say you want to find data on "Agro-industry farming."
    
**HTTP Request:**
`http://docs.endangeredanimals.apiary.io/single_threat_data/?q=Agro-industry farming`

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Body
    
            {
                "name": "Agro-industry farming",
                "timing": "ongoing",
                "severity":"3",
                "assoc_animals": [
                    "African Elephant",
                    "Kangaroo"
                ], 
                "assoc_habitats": [
                    "Desert - Temperate",
                    "Desert - Hot"
                ]
            }

