## Country [/single_country_data]

### /single_country_data/?q=COUNTRY  [GET]

Retrieves data for a specific country: name, flag, coordinates, and associated animals/threats/habitats.

Example: Let's say you want to find data on "Albania."

**HTTP Request:**
`http://docs.endangeredanimals.apiary.io/single_country_data/?q=Albania`

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Body
    
            {
                "name": "Albania",
                "flag": "http://cdn.wonderfulengineering.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/Albania-Flag-6.png",
